OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FBright
OL,6,Fspells with scattered showers in the
OL,7,Fevening, these clearing away
OL,8,Fnorthwards. Briefly dry before
OL,9,Fbecoming cloudy with rain outbreaks of
OL,10,Frain spreading east later.
OL,11,
OL,12,CSaturday:FCloudy with rain at times.
OL,13,FThe rain will be mainly light but a
OL,14,Ffew isolated heavy showers may develop
OL,15,Ffrom late afternoon.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
